Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:05:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉玛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.33,0:06:02.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:03.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.78,0:06:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是中央集散中心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都是邮差吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.09,0:06:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们将四处收集到的货物暂时集中在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.27,0:06:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后领取自己负责投递的那份
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.37,0:06:31.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.76,0:06:32.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.30,0:06:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅露蒂 纱雅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:37.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作习惯了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.47,0:06:40.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都知道该怎么做了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.63,0:06:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…正在一点一点地学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:43.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:47.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有艾米前辈的指导 马上就能学会的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.79,0:06:49.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.08,0:06:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是下午需要投递的份！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.23,0:06:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:06:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够三个人分工真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.76,0:07:00.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久没有分在同一个区了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢 就来问我说像我这样的女孩会想要什么礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.43,0:07:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会想要鞋子呢 因为很快就会磨破
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.90,0:07:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.15,0:07:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是说他把我往哪搁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.28,0:07:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 应该说他心思不够细腻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.13,0:07:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种人就别管了呗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.42,0:07:22.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出现了 有男朋友的人就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.81,0:07:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.76,0:07:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那个给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:27.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 分完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.73,0:07:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样细分之后 配送起来也会比较轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:32.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.46,0:07:34.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我们出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.14,0:07:47.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这附近的船我还没全部记住呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:53.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这附近都是我之前所在的舰团的船 所以我很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.15,0:08:02.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 那边是我家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.73,0:08:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 挺不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 过来一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.33,0:08:18.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.33,0:08:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 很危险的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:47.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外行人别靠近这东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱 抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.45,0:08:50.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 麦塔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.91,0:08:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉玛 不可以打扰别人工作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.23,0:08:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 你是技师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.48,0:08:58.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 这里是怎么加工的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:04.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合金的比率是多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.68,0:09:06.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,促动器的扭矩有多大？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.68,0:09:06.64,ruby,NTP,0,310,0,,actuator
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.76,0:09:13.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么喜欢机械的话就来我这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:15.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近一段时间很缺人手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.50,0:09:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说皮尼欧 你说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.76,0:09:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 飞机头先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.27,0:09:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.15,0:09:26.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我现在想更多了解加尔刚蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:43.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.38,0:09:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亏你们能找到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这艘船就以将整个船体拉起来的方针来打捞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:55.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为接收了库盖尔舰团的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以现在必须增加船只的数量才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.15,0:09:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那艘船相当大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.07,0:10:00.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捞起来后放哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.65,0:10:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会让库罗诺亚号的农场尽快结束收割的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.41,0:10:06.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放那里应该没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.24,0:10:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:11.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次可是大阵仗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:23.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 久等了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.67,0:10:29.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走吧 我都一身汗了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作后泡个澡真是爽翻了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.03,0:10:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呦 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:10:59.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说你发现的沉船决定打捞上来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.73,0:11:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.94,0:11:05.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我的秘密武器要得到久违的出场机会了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:07.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密武器？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.43,0:11:10.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 等着瞧吧 保证你吓破胆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 在库盖尔舰团里相当于是莉玛为我带路的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:22.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 年纪轻轻的却很能干呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.37,0:11:23.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.98,0:11:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还「年纪轻轻」…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.34,0:11:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家不就只比你小一岁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.45,0:11:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 你们都在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.69,0:11:34.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.20,0:11:38.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米 今天雷德立大功了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.86,0:11:39.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.21,0:11:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过他刚才没跟我说这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.53,0:11:45.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 你们又一起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是恩爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加尔刚蒂亚上还真是有不少不错的设备呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.21,0:12:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婆婆 我要海藻混合饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.04,0:12:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.31,0:12:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.58,0:12:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 原大海贼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们真失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.35,0:12:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我休假中的大海贼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.55,0:12:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然自己这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.57,0:12:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且休假要暂时结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:20.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近期会有一次大型打捞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了防止被打扰 由我们负责开道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:29.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是所谓的保镖工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.48,0:12:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真意外
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.63,0:12:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你有在认真工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.35,0:12:33.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:43.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是雷德？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.98,0:12:47.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫莉玛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.52,0:12:49.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在接受艾米的工作指导
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.77,0:12:51.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快递方面的工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.35,0:12:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.34,0:12:58.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所乘坐的会飞的人形机器人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说Chamber？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.31,0:13:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.57,0:13:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:13.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用于战斗的机械
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.25,0:13:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,操纵重力在空中飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.74,0:13:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以理解语言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论在任何时刻 都会凭借强大力量保护驾驶员的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.71,0:13:26.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最强的铠甲 Machine Caliber
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.97,0:13:34.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是Chamber
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:40.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的和天神的使者一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.65,0:13:42.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 天神…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.17,0:13:47.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的是Striker吗？库盖尔中校所乘坐的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.49,0:13:51.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我来自于库盖尔大人的舰团
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.76,0:13:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.59,0:13:56.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 可以告诉我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.15,0:13:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中校和Striker到底出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.87,0:14:01.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.91,0:14:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现了帅哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么什么 转移目标了？劈腿？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.31,0:14:09.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 莉玛的心情倒也可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:10.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.47,0:14:18.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 如果得不到百分之百的关注 少女可是会不安的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.68,0:14:20.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错没错 艾米她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.47,0:14:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 她都悄悄去找Chamber商量了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.99,0:14:36.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说…雷德有没有什么想要的东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:38.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chamber？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.00,0:14:46.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少尉所需要的食物和生活物资现在都得到了稳定的供给
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.02,0:14:48.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.91,0:14:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…该怎么说呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.08,0:14:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是指他收到了会觉得高兴的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.93,0:14:56.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让他露出笑脸的东西…之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.80,0:15:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经判明同盟标准的娱乐程序对少尉没有任何效果
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.99,0:15:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个也不对啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.69,0:15:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎样才能更了解雷德呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.80,0:15:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为 为…为什么你们会知道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.50,0:15:20.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.12,0:15:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是建议啦 建议…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.30,0:15:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事用不着啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.06,0:15:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾…艾米？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:29.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了怎么了 争风吃醋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.96,0:15:30.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年轻真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.21,0:15:32.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令人莞尔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.48,0:15:34.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 一个个都这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.65,0:15:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生活充实是件好事 不过工作那边怎么样啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.64,0:15:41.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打捞虽然不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:44.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你也是时候觉得摆弄机械很有趣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.27,0:15:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…等等 皮尼欧 你什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:51.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮尼欧常常会教我关于人形机器人构造方面的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.50,0:15:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可怜他天天被甲壳屁股责骂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.59,0:16:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}谁是甲壳屁股啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.34,0:16:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.55,0:16:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉玛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:02.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.77,0:16:11.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都想知道中校所率领的舰团为什么会变成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.43,0:16:13.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:26.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在库盖尔大人和使者大人开始引导人们的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:30.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的船加入了他们的舰团
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.16,0:16:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰团上下将库盖尔大人奉为天神的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.21,0:16:36.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从而团结了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.82,0:16:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在利用鲸乌贼制造的叛乱结束之后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.15,0:16:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽娜莉亚大人和艾蕾莉亚大人死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.30,0:16:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的一切都发生了改变
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.43,0:16:51.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个人都要为维持舰团献出自己的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:55.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连死也不过是其中的一种手段
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.33,0:16:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了维持强大而舍弃弱者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.47,0:17:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强迫无法战斗的人牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.95,0:17:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灌输为集体献身才是幸福的思想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.28,0:17:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这正是人类银河同盟的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.78,0:17:13.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不认为中校渴望那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.33,0:17:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.59,0:17:22.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有任何人知道库盖尔大人到底是什么时候死去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:26.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果中校活着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.52,0:17:29.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果应该不会是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.29,0:17:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所认识的中校 曾经无数次拯救过我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.28,0:17:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 没找到相关的资料呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.62,0:17:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调查Chamber的事很不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.20,0:17:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为能从留下的操纵席上了解一些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:18:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但它所使用的技术还是远远超过了旧文明的水准
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.46,0:18:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲留给妹妹丽娜莉亚的书籍已经全都在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:12.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉 没帮上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.27,0:18:14.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:18.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些书里有很多加尔刚蒂亚上没有的知识
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.34,0:18:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得知这颗星球将会成为冰封的星球之后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.89,0:18:25.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类分裂成两大阵营开始了斗争
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.94,0:18:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但同时也有一小群人试图探寻其他的出路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.24,0:18:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就是那些人的后代
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.68,0:18:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个人都放下了矜持 不顾一切地想要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.77,0:18:45.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在斗争的同时启程奔向星河世界的人们应该也是如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说 那些人抛弃了地球吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.43,0:18:55.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是如此 我也更愿意相信他们是有过一番挣扎的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.00,0:19:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离开了地球的人们后来的境遇如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.48,0:19:31.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里只有我一个人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得 应该有些事是只有知情的我才能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.01,0:19:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在寻找是否有能与鲸乌贼交流的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.23,0:19:45.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是否有能更加和平地 从容地共存的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.22,0:19:50.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这就像是我个人的赎罪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.72,0:19:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你必须抱有这种心情才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.18,0:19:59.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米 我一直都在害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.21,0:20:00.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.00,0:20:06.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同盟现在也还在和希迪亚斯进行着殊死的全面战争吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.42,0:20:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我隐约认为这是无可奈何的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…你现在不是在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.00,0:20:18.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前所在的宇宙在很远的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.21,0:20:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就没必要那样去想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.70,0:20:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那已经和你没有任何关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.56,0:20:27.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这全都是相关的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.48,0:20:30.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些都是人类的所为
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.01,0:20:40.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们与鲸乌贼为敌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.27,0:20:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么当希迪亚斯来到地球的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.78,0:20:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的想法和同盟会是不同的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.11,0:20:50.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是否会已经找到了其他的道路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.78,0:20:54.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.52,0:20:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了活下去而必须舍弃无法替代的东西的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.11,0:21:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 不会发生那种事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.67,0:21:13.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你无论何时…就连那时…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连那个暴风雨的日子 你也和Chamber一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.09,0:21:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴风雨的日子…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:32.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉玛 你都听到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.55,0:21:34.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是有意的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.65,0:21:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我说谎了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.10,0:21:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.88,0:21:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 可以的话请告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.22,0:21:44.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那场暴风雨中 雷德和Chamber怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.94,0:22:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚被冲走的船又被冲回来撞上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.31,0:22:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有进水吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.39,0:22:08.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经放下隔离壁了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.06,0:22:09.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.04,0:22:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保险起见 还是要确认一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.95,0:22:32.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是这个区域的最后一艘了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.69,0:22:33.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.92,0:22:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白 开始工作
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.63,0:22:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接上了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.13,0:22:45.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.98,0:22:46.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起重机开动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.54,0:22:55.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各连接部位无异常
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.11,0:22:58.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 就这样继续警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.66,0:22:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.62,0:23:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.89,0:23:18.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧急联络！与阿尔特弥亚号之间的连接濒临脱落！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.89,0:23:18.81,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}注：阿尔特弥亚（Artemia） 俗称丰年虾、卤虫、海猴子等
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.46,0:23:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.57,0:23:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报告详情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.83,0:23:27.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辅助钢索全部绷断 连接器也损坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.54,0:23:29.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一部还完好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.49,0:23:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 两舷的汽艇都无法使用？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.49,0:23:33.97,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,screw boat
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.15,0:23:42.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰团长 阿尔特弥亚号上有500多位居民
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.76,0:23:43.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.78,0:23:45.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联络桥呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.39,0:23:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然还有一架完好 但不知道能撑到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.08,0:23:51.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有办法修吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.15,0:23:56.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忙不过来 迅速修理应该是不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.34,0:24:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邮件来了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.89,0:24:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是被害情况的…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.92,0:24:16.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让无法控制的中型船漂流会让整个舰团也陷入危险
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.10,0:24:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炸沉阿尔特弥亚号
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.41,0:24:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔特弥亚号…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.89,0:24:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.78,0:24:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将阿尔特弥亚号全员退舰作为最优先事项
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.50,0:24:36.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炸沉阿尔特弥亚号
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.82,0:24:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧进行引导！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.15,0:24:40.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纱雅的船…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.31,0:24:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.36,0:24:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别慌张！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.54,0:24:59.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.86,0:25:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…纱雅呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.41,0:25:02.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐还…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.63,0:25:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.16,0:25:12.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.20,0:25:15.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要炸沉的话我也一起死在这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.25,0:25:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船长 别撒娇了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.50,0:25:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}我死都不会走的！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.84,0:25:20.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带他走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.30,0:25:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船长 我们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.23,0:25:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.88,0:25:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妹妹在四处确认居民的撤离情况
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.73,0:25:30.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也撤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.62,0:25:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗莱斯
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.08,0:25:37.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舵转不动 死待在舰桥上也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.98,0:25:39.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 快撤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.83,0:25:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 这里是舰桥
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.91,0:25:49.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 到中央船舱为止的居民已经都撤走了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.34,0:25:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 舰桥也只剩下我一个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.50,0:25:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧时间确认剩余的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.33,0:25:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.91,0:25:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纱雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.32,0:25:56.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米…你怎么来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.51,0:25:59.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说要弃船所以我很担心
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.89,0:26:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在确认船上还有没有人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.33,0:26:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也来帮忙 还剩下哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.20,0:26:05.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船首舱和船尾舱
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.00,0:26:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我去船首舱
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.89,0:26:08.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.07,0:26:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 要放弃阿尔特弥亚号是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.11,0:26:23.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 现在正在组织退舰
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.81,0:26:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.25,0:26:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.17,0:26:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上离开这艘船！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.34,0:26:35.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.40,0:26:36.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.49,0:26:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧时间！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.75,0:26:39.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往这边走
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.85,0:26:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.23,0:26:44.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.15,0:26:50.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.19,0:26:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩下我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.74,0:26:53.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.33,0:26:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等自沉处理完成后 我们也撤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.04,0:26:58.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的只能这么做了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.12,0:27:00.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然要弃船…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.01,0:27:02.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舵不能用了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.94,0:27:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只靠一部连接器的话 这艘船可能会撞上舰团
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.19,0:27:09.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能在事态演变成这样之前把船炸沉
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.09,0:27:13.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里可是我们成长的家呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.75,0:27:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种大风暴我也从来都没见过
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.84,0:27:22.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过人生在世 无能为力的事总是难免
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.22,0:27:27.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是阿尔特弥亚号
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.48,0:27:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨浪正在接近！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.97,0:27:30.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点 快点去避难！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.08,0:27:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅露蒂？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.07,0:27:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听不太清楚 再说一遍！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.01,0:27:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.72,0:27:35.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看那边！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.85,0:28:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都没事吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.67,0:28:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.23,0:28:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.54,0:28:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.79,0:28:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.22,0:28:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,检测到船舶的过度倾斜
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.46,0:28:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chamber！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.23,0:28:37.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米 纱雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.60,0:28:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.29,0:28:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没事
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.44,0:29:01.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.85,0:29:04.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经突破极限倾斜角度！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.30,0:29:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chamber 最大功率！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.74,0:29:12.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.67,0:29:21.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 钢索呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.20,0:29:24.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在撑着 能行！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.76,0:29:26.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 拉起来！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.66,0:29:27.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.68,0:29:38.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好！加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.80,0:29:41.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 这可糟了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.61,0:29:47.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.69,0:29:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 艾米…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.46,0:30:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接收到紧急通信
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.25,0:30:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家听我说！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.88,0:30:04.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔特弥亚号被冲走了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.97,0:30:07.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纱雅和艾米还在上面！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.47,0:30:09.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.58,0:30:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该船舶的运行控制已失效 推测已经无法掌舵
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.33,0:30:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在漂流吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.98,0:30:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.89,0:30:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.18,0:30:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在又不能离开这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.22,0:30:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 要撑住啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.76,0:30:31.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还差一点！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.35,0:30:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 破废铁
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.33,0:30:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回里面去！穿上这个！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.49,0:30:46.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.57,0:30:52.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟 糟了 船正在往回飘
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.86,0:31:04.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船体开始恢复平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.73,0:31:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去了 船体开始恢复直立了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.59,0:31:11.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倾斜角度逐渐减小
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.76,0:31:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推测正在转入安定状态
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.27,0:31:14.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.83,0:32:01.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.61,0:32:04.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威胁级别 下调
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.82,0:32:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来发生过这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.26,0:32:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时是因为有Chamber
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.72,0:32:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那家伙已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.49,0:32:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 就算现在发生了同样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.78,0:32:29.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德也肯定不会放弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.65,0:32:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为总是为自己所能做到的事竭尽全力
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.58,0:32:37.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你的为人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.42,0:33:19.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 开始下沉
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.69,0:33:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝罗兹 捕捞框正常下降
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.65,0:33:35.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 大家都听到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.03,0:33:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来要让一艘船从墓场中复生
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.90,0:33:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是宝贝中的宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.00,0:33:43.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好把它捞上来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.97,0:33:44.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.95,0:33:54.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认周边的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.19,0:34:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮尼欧 有你的信
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.06,0:34:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.88,0:34:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？你不用接着去送货吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.72,0:34:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的工作到此就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.24,0:34:23.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,担心雷德吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.57,0:34:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 不…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.28,0:34:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ok 就这样保持警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.18,0:34:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮尼欧 放出固定锚
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.21,0:34:41.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好咧！
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.33,0:34:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 你们几个准备好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.45,0:34:52.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 我们开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.63,0:34:56.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一班 将引导钢索连接到船体上
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.25,0:35:10.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二班 将主钢索从船底绕过
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.07,0:35:12.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认连接情况！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.00,0:35:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认完毕！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.64,0:35:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入最后工序了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.93,0:35:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.33,0:35:18.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.40,0:35:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.44,0:35:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢索好像被什么给勾住了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.84,0:35:45.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.92,0:35:48.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要崩塌了！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.12,0:35:50.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧点 赶快！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.88,0:36:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 有我撑着！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.32,0:36:05.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.86,0:36:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.83,0:36:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德还在下面！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.05,0:36:29.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.82,0:36:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切断钢索的连接！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.49,0:36:38.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.82,0:36:42.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.48,0:37:24.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,氧气存量！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.85,0:37:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.44,0:37:29.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,备用氧气罐打开
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.12,0:37:32.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二氧化碳吸收剂紧急投入
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.77,0:37:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电池存量已确认
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.77,0:37:35.18,ruby,NTP,0,230,0,,battery
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.36,0:37:37.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,控制器正常
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.36,0:37:37.19,ruby,NTP,0,110,0,,Manipulator
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.51,0:37:41.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认通信状态
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.46,0:37:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.28,0:37:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说通信缆线…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.63,0:37:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 谁来回句话！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.24,0:37:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.25,0:37:56.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是雷德！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.65,0:38:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面到底发生了什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.05,0:38:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.46,0:38:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然有瓦斯涌出来 周边崩塌了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.95,0:38:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德那小子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.18,0:38:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算还活着 备用氧气也该用尽了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.38,0:38:29.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…那就快点潜回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.30,0:38:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在接近那里太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.87,0:38:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救助队也会被卷入进去
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.33,0:38:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.76,0:38:38.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.33,0:38:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能想想办法吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.91,0:38:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝罗兹…！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.52,0:38:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝罗兹！我说！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.10,0:38:56.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有应答
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.74,0:39:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是Machine Caliber K6821驾驶员 雷德少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.30,0:39:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.39,0:39:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有应答
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.66,0:39:09.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推测由于希迪亚斯的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.30,0:39:12.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导致整个机库处于漂流状态
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.58,0:39:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧给我恢复通信 你这废物！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.89,0:39:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,建议关闭电波发射机能
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.62,0:39:19.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.95,0:39:22.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认到多数希迪亚斯的生体反应
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.91,0:39:25.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本机有被探知的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.19,0:39:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.04,0:39:36.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就只能等着被它们吞噬吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.67,0:39:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快发出求救信号！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.67,0:39:41.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么可能相信你这种机器的判断！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.86,0:39:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.24,0:39:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有判断都由专属驾驶员雷德少尉进行
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.51,0:39:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵官能力的充分发挥
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.68,0:39:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可使本机导出打开局面的最佳方法
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.80,0:40:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说你的威力取决于我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.08,0:40:08.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定 期待贵官做出明智的判断
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.54,0:40:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.93,0:40:13.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能死在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.57,0:40:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是你还是我 都一定要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.68,0:40:18.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同意
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.44,0:40:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是驾驶员支援启发连接系统
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.37,0:40:29.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让贵官获得更多的成果便是我的存在意义所在
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.59,0:40:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.88,0:40:38.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时 他让我要相信自己的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.37,0:40:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且他说他相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.49,0:40:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西也撑不了太久
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.02,0:40:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想想 快想想！
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.84,0:41:48.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再多来点 把在这的家伙都拉过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.96,0:41:52.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,储气瓶不够 能搬多少来就搬多少来
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.96,0:41:52.44,ruby,NTP,0,540,0,,Bombe
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.45,0:41:56.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就得这样才行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.73,0:42:02.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,召集各位船主
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.50,0:42:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向他们请求人力和物资协助
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.22,0:42:08.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 安排医疗队
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.65,0:42:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.21,0:42:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.62,0:42:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去救他！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.82,0:42:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉玛？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.57,0:42:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬请期待
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.67,0:42:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.26,0:42:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.30,0:42:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.22,0:42:40.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.67,0:42:42.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也应该能帮上什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.25,0:42:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说傻话了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.59,0:42:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该做的是另一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.76,0:42:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.83,0:42:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用笑脸去迎接这些不要命的傻瓜们和雷德的归来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.33,0:42:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会平安带他回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.13,0:42:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.17,0:43:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么说定了！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.74,0:43:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在这里面
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.13,0:43:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没找到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.18,0:43:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉凯奇？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.66,0:43:53.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你们慢吞吞的搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.70,0:43:55.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.43,0:44:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都有我在附近了还在这种地方搞出死人来
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.70,0:44:09.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是存心想让我睡不好觉么
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.04,0:44:10.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉凯奇？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.99,0:44:14.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪块地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.77,0:44:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这缝隙里面
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.37,0:44:20.28,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,Amigo
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.37,0:44:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伙计
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.74,0:44:22.29,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,Storonzo
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.74,0:44:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去你妈的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.29,0:44:35.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.57,0:44:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好拉凯奇 就这么撑住
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.37,0:44:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了！
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.42,0:44:55.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还活着！
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.82,0:44:57.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.42,0:45:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把浮筒用的压缩空气释放到驾驶舱里了吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.46,0:45:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有你的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.29,0:45:09.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了 雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.38,0:45:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会互相配合 同时把这里撑开
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.27,0:45:15.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就在这个瞬间把四肢和浮筒从躯干部分离
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.83,0:45:18.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机会只有一次
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.68,0:45:19.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信同伴！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.50,0:45:23.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.38,0:45:33.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒数3下就开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.50,0:45:35.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.60,0:45:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.81,0:45:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.06,0:45:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抬起来！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.82,0:45:49.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在 雷德！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.53,0:45:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.99,0:46:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机体从里面出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.09,0:46:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德平安无事！
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.83,0:46:16.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.21,0:46:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.64,0:46:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.26,0:46:53.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.95,0:46:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.66,0:47:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.31,0:47:03.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.56,0:47:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米 我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.13,0:47:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.01,0:49:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 进入下一个阶段
Comment: 0,0:49:22.65,0:49:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解【这句其实我听不懂…………我觉得应该是外星语吧Orz
